ZH: 这艘驱逐舰可以携带数十枚反舰导弹。
EN: This destroyer can carry dozens of anti-ship missiles.

ZH: 那些驱逐舰组成了强大的海军编队。
EN: Those destroyers form a powerful naval fleet.

ZH: 他在海军驱逐舰上担任了五年的舰长。
EN: He served as captain on a naval destroyer for five years.

ZH: 联合演习中派出了数艘驱逐舰进行护航任务。
EN: Several destroyers were dispatched for escort duties during the joint exercise.

ZH: 我们的新一代驱逐舰在性能上有较大提升。
EN: Our new generation of destroyers has significantly improved in performance.

ZH: 驱逐舰在危急时刻可以提供有效的火力支援。
EN: Destroyers can provide effective fire support in critical situations.

ZH: 海军正派遣驱逐舰前往执行护航任务。
EN: The navy is dispatching destroyers to carry out escort missions.

ZH: 这次军演中使用了模拟驱逐舰进行对抗演练。
EN: Simulated destroyers were used in the exercise for confrontation drills.

ZH: 驱逐舰的主要任务是打击敌方水面舰艇。
EN: The primary mission of destroyers is to strike enemy surface ships.

ZH: 这支驱逐舰编队在敌方侦察机出现后迅速躲避。
EN: This destroyer fleet quickly evaded after enemy reconnaissance aircraft appeared.

ZH: 驱逐舰担负起了保护舰队的重要角色。
EN: Destroyers play a crucial role in protecting the fleet.

ZH: 舰队司令下令驱逐舰立即起航前往事发地点。
EN: The fleet commander ordered the destroyer to set sail immediately to the scene.

ZH: 驱逐舰的雷达系统可以探测到远处的敌方舰艇。
EN: The radar system on the destroyer can detect enemy ships from afar.

ZH: 他们在黑夜中靠近了驱逐舰，准备发动突袭。
EN: They approached the destroyer in the dark, ready to launch a raid.

ZH: 驱逐舰展开了搜索行动，希望找到失踪的船只。
EN: The destroyer launched a search operation in hopes of finding the missing vessel.

ZH: 驱逐舰的机动性和火力使其成为多种任务的首选舰艇。
EN: The maneuverability and firepower of destroyers make them the preferred vessels for various tasks.

ZH: 驱逐舰在对抗潜艇方面有着独特的优势。
EN: Destroyers have unique advantages in combating submarines.

ZH: 这艘驱逐舰已经服役了十年，依然状态良好。
EN: This destroyer has been in service for ten years and is still in good condition.

ZH: 这支驱逐舰编队将前往南海执行巡逻任务。
EN: This destroyer fleet will head to the South China Sea to carry out patrol missions.

ZH: 情报显示敌方正酝酿一次大规模的驱逐舰袭击。
EN: Intelligence indicates that the enemy is planning a large-scale destroyer attack.
